$interpreted: Illegal Miner Foreman: I heard rumors of a golem wandering around here. Looks like we just confirmed it!
Illegal Miner: Hah! Saves us a trip to Totemtaff!
Illegal Miner Foreman: Quick, get the gems on its back. We're gonna be rich!
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~~!
Vanessa: Calm down, big guy. I'm on your side.
Vanessa: Don't worry, I won't hurt you.
Vanessa: Now, now, I'll back off and you do the same...
Golemwalt: Grrou!?
Vanessa: Here, mud balls made with mud from Totemtaff. Smell like home, huh?
Vanessa: Take your time, I'll heal you up.
Golemwalt: Rroouu!!!
Vanessa: You feeling better?
Golemwalt: Grrrrr......
Vanessa: My, my. Now that I've bought you dinner, can't we at least be friends?
Vanessa: I'm Vanessa from the Rare Creature Conservation Society. We specialize in observing and protecting rare animals like you.
Vanessa: We heard about a wandering golem on the border of Paradise Prairie and Totemtaff Ridge. I was sent to see what was up.
Vanessa: Ended up spotting you. Why'd you leave Totemtaff?
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~~
Vanessa: Silly me, you can't talk...
Vanessa: I guess I should find you a place to lay low around here first. I'll escort you back home once there's an opportunity.
Golemwalt: ...*burp*...
Vanessa: Heh, you look just like Walt when you burp.
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~?
Vanessa: Right, I should probably give you a name, since we'll be together for a while...
Vanessa: You're a golem, and you burp like Walt... I guess I'll call you Golemwalt!
Golemwalt: Grrrooouuu~?
Vanessa: Who's Walt? Heh, I'll tell you when we get to know each other a bit better.
Vanessa: You know, Golemwalt, you actually made the right decision back there when you attacked me.
Vanessa: There are a lot of evil people in this world. Don't trust strangers too easily, understand?
